trans-unit.source: Represents a collection of <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.OperationInput"></xref> and <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.OperationOutput"></xref> messages related to an XML Web service.
trans-unit.target: Representa uma coleção de <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.OperationInput"> </xref> e <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.OperationOutput"> </xref> mensagens relacionadas a um serviço Web XML.

trans-unit.source: This class cannot be inherited.
trans-unit.target: Essa classe não pode ser herdada.

trans-unit.source: An instance of this class will be returned by the <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.Operation.Messages%2A> property of the parent <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.Operation>.
trans-unit.target: Uma instância desta classe será retornada pela <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.Operation.Messages%2A>propriedade do pai <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.Operation>.</xref:System.Web.Services.Description.Operation> </xref:System.Web.Services.Description.Operation.Messages%2A>

trans-unit.source: As such, it can have exactly two members, one an <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.OperationInput> and the other an <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.OperationOutput>.
trans-unit.target: Como tal, ele pode ter exatamente dois membros, um <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.OperationInput>e outro <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.OperationOutput>.</xref:System.Web.Services.Description.OperationOutput> </xref:System.Web.Services.Description.OperationInput>

trans-unit.source: The zero-based index where the operationMessage parameter has been added.

trans-unit.source: Copies the entire <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.OperationMessageCollection"></xref> to a compatible one-dimensional array of type <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.OperationMessage"></xref>, starting at the specified zero-based index of the target array.
trans-unit.target: Copia todo o <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.OperationMessageCollection"> </xref> para uma matriz unidimensional compatível do tipo <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.OperationMessage"> </xref>, começando no índice de base zero especificado da matriz de destino.

trans-unit.source: An array of type <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.OperationMessage"></xref> serving as the destination for the copy action.
trans-unit.target: Uma matriz do tipo <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.OperationMessage"> </xref> que serve como o destino para a ação de cópia.

trans-unit.source: The zero-based index at which to start placing the copied collection.
trans-unit.target: O índice baseado em zero no qual começar a colocar a coleção copiada.

trans-unit.source: Gets the type of transmission supported by the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.OperationMessageCollection"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Obtém o tipo de transmissão com suporte a <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.OperationMessageCollection"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: One of the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.OperationFlow"></xref> values.
trans-unit.target: Uma da <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.OperationFlow"> </xref> valores.

trans-unit.source: The default is <xref uid="langword_csharp_SolicitResponse" name="SolicitResponse" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: O padrão é <xref uid="langword_csharp_SolicitResponse" name="SolicitResponse" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Searches for the specified <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.OperationMessage"></xref> and returns the zero-based index of the first occurrence within the collection.
trans-unit.target: Procura especificado <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.OperationMessage"> </xref> e retorna o índice baseado em zero da primeira ocorrência na coleção.

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.OperationMessage"></xref> for which to search in the collection.
trans-unit.target: O <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.OperationMessage"> </xref> ser pesquisado na coleção.

trans-unit.source: The zero-based index of the specified operation message, or -1 if the element was not found in the collection.
trans-unit.target: O índice com base em zero da mensagem de operação especificado, ou -1 se o elemento não foi encontrado na coleção.

trans-unit.source: Gets the first occurrence of an <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.OperationInput"></xref> within the collection.
trans-unit.target: Obtém a primeira ocorrência de um <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.OperationInput"> </xref> dentro da coleção.

trans-unit.target: Um <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.OperationInput"> </xref> dentro da coleção.

trans-unit.source: Adds the specified <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.OperationMessage"></xref> to the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.OperationMessageCollection"></xref> at the specified zero-based index.
trans-unit.target: Adiciona o <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.OperationMessage"> </xref> para o <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.OperationMessageCollection"> </xref> no índice de base zero especificado.

trans-unit.source: If the number of items in the collection already equals the collection's capacity, the capacity is doubled by automatically reallocating the internal array before the new element is inserted.
trans-unit.target: Se o número de itens na coleção já for igual a capacidade da coleção, a capacidade é duplicada, automaticamente realocando a matriz interna antes do novo elemento é inserido.

trans-unit.source: If the `index` parameter is equal to <xref:System.Collections.CollectionBase.Count%2A>, the `operationMessage` parameter is added to the end of the collection.
trans-unit.target: Se o `index` parâmetro for igual ao <xref:System.Collections.CollectionBase.Count%2A>, o `operationMessage` parâmetro é adicionado ao final da coleção.</xref:System.Collections.CollectionBase.Count%2A>

trans-unit.source: The elements after the insertion point move down to accommodate the new element.
trans-unit.target: Os elementos após o ponto de inserção se mover para baixo para acomodar o novo elemento.

trans-unit.source: The zero-based index at which to insert the `operationMessage` parameter.
trans-unit.target: O índice de base zero no qual inserir o `operationMessage` parâmetro.

trans-unit.target: Obtém ou define o valor de um <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.OperationMessage"> </xref> no índice de base zero especificado.
